1
00:00:01,014 --> 00:00:03,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"This story is fiction.</b></font>

2
00:00:01,014 --> 00:00:03,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}All names of characters, places and</b></font>

3
00:00:01,014 --> 00:00:03,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}organizations in the story are fictional.</b></font>

4
00:00:01,014 --> 00:00:03,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}Follow the traffic rules and drive safely."</b></font>

5
00:00:14,454 --> 00:00:17,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Get ready, yo! Now we blow up the horn</i></b></font>

6
00:00:30,744 --> 00:00:34,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>In the silver smoke amidst the frozen city</i></b></font>

7
00:00:34,474 --> 00:00:38,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Payback for a dream I've seen so many times</i></b></font>

8
00:00:38,144 --> 00:00:41,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My body is frozen in a</i>
<i>memory that I can't shake</i></b></font>

9
00:00:41,814 --> 00:00:45,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Slam on the accelerator and deceive myself</i></b></font>

10
00:00:45,584 --> 00:00:48,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Broken in the night</i></b></font>

11
00:00:48,724 --> 00:00:52,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My eyes become sharper</i></b></font>

12
00:00:52,924 --> 00:00:56,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>All from someone's whim</i></b></font>

13
00:00:56,064 --> 00:01:00,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It seems like the world will end any minute</i></b></font>

14
00:01:00,304 --> 00:01:02,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Break into the night, it's the time</i></b></font>

15
00:01:02,174 --> 00:01:05,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>With scared eyes, I'm lost in the night</i></b></font>

16
00:01:05,844 --> 00:01:09,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Embraced by a falling dream</i></b></font>

17
00:01:09,474 --> 00:01:13,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Scared of being alone, missin' my heart</i></b></font>

18
00:01:13,114 --> 00:01:16,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Even hurting myself</i></b></font>

19
00:01:16,924 --> 00:01:20,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Love me so much,</i>
<i>enough that I could fall apart</i></b></font>

20
00:01:20,624 --> 00:01:24,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If only I could throw everything away</i></b></font>

21
00:01:24,264 --> 00:01:27,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And just love you</i></b></font>

22
00:01:27,934 --> 00:01:32,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Then I know I could face the truth</i></b></font>

23
00:01:35,534 --> 00:01:38,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Vroom!</b></font>

24
00:01:38,474 --> 00:01:41,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And at the corner I went...</b></font>

25
00:01:41,014 --> 00:01:43,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Voosh!</b></font>

26
00:01:43,844 --> 00:01:45,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...as I cleared it.</b></font>

27
00:01:45,144 --> 00:01:48,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At that moment, I was like the wind.</b></font>

28
00:01:48,654 --> 00:01:51,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nothing beats the pass.</b></font>

29
00:01:51,154 --> 00:01:55,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When you have your own cars, go check it out.</b></font>

30
00:01:55,194 --> 00:01:59,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My car? It's an Eight-Five,
every racer's dream car!</b></font>

31
00:01:59,524 --> 00:02:02,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You probably didn't know that.</b></font>

32
00:02:06,664 --> 00:02:12,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Act 21: Challenge from a Superstar"</b></font>

33
00:02:12,674 --> 00:02:17,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This summer was very memorable.</b></font>

34
00:02:17,584 --> 00:02:20,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Why?
--"Why?"</b></font>

35
00:02:20,014 --> 00:02:22,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Because I bought a car,</b></font>

36
00:02:22,014 --> 00:02:26,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and you debuted in the
racing world like a comet.</b></font>

37
00:02:26,054 --> 00:02:28,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't tease me like that.</b></font>

38
00:02:28,254 --> 00:02:30,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>One, two, three, four...</b></font>

39
00:02:30,664 --> 00:02:31,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you counting?</b></font>

40
00:02:31,994 --> 00:02:37,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Four is the number of
races you won this summer.</b></font>

41
00:02:37,234 --> 00:02:40,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>First, Keisuke Takahashi of the Red Suns' FD.</b></font>

42
00:02:49,044 --> 00:02:52,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Second, Nakazato of the Night Kids' R32.</b></font>

43
00:03:03,354 --> 00:03:08,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Third, the duct tape death match
with Shingo Shoji's EG6.</b></font>

44
00:03:17,104 --> 00:03:22,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Finally, Mako and Sayuki's
Sileighty at Usui Pass.</b></font>

45
00:03:29,784 --> 00:03:31,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Four for four.</b></font>

46
00:03:31,284 --> 00:03:35,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your undefeated legend began this summer.</b></font>

47
00:03:35,394 --> 00:03:39,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're no longer just a dummy.</b></font>

48
00:03:39,464 --> 00:03:42,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Stop exaggerating.</b></font>

49
00:03:42,064 --> 00:03:43,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't be embarrassed!</b></font>

50
00:03:43,564 --> 00:03:46,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keep winning, Takumi!</b></font>

51
00:03:46,004 --> 00:03:48,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Until I beat you,</b></font>

52
00:03:48,474 --> 00:03:53,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and become the fastest in Gunma--
no, in all of Kanto!</b></font>

53
00:03:53,144 --> 00:03:58,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They'll be calling me... "Itsuki, Akina's Comet"!</b></font>

54
00:03:58,184 --> 00:03:59,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh?</b></font>

55
00:04:01,514 --> 00:04:05,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Since school ends early today,</b></font>

56
00:04:05,024 --> 00:04:07,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>let's go do something in the afternoon.</b></font>

57
00:04:08,624 --> 00:04:11,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I kind of have to work in the afternoon.</b></font>

58
00:04:11,924 --> 00:04:14,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What? You do?</b></font>

59
00:04:14,134 --> 00:04:18,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want to ride in your car again...</b></font>

60
00:04:18,604 --> 00:04:20,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...because it's very cute.</b></font>

61
00:04:20,034 --> 00:04:25,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you say so... but it's my dad's car.</b></font>

62
00:04:25,504 --> 00:04:28,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You said you wanted to buy a car.</b></font>

63
00:04:28,174 --> 00:04:31,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you saving up?</b></font>

64
00:04:31,144 --> 00:04:33,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I save most of what I make,</b></font>

65
00:04:33,984 --> 00:04:35,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I'm still far from it.</b></font>

66
00:04:35,984 --> 00:04:38,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How much do you need?</b></font>

67
00:04:38,324 --> 00:04:41,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Around a million yen.</b></font>

68
00:04:41,824 --> 00:04:44,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A million...</b></font>

69
00:04:44,494 --> 00:04:46,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How much do you have now?</b></font>

70
00:04:46,494 --> 00:04:48,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not even close.</b></font>

71
00:04:50,464 --> 00:04:52,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi?</b></font>

72
00:04:52,664 --> 00:04:56,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What would you do if I gave you the money?</b></font>

73
00:04:56,804 --> 00:04:59,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder...</b></font>

74
00:04:59,874 --> 00:05:01,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I bet you'd thank me,</b></font>

75
00:05:01,544 --> 00:05:05,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and treat me like a princess.</b></font>

76
00:05:05,544 --> 00:05:08,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You'd owe me big,</b></font>

77
00:05:08,714 --> 00:05:12,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so you'd have to quit working</b></font>

78
00:05:12,054 --> 00:05:14,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and take care of me and love me every day!</b></font>

79
00:05:14,524 --> 00:05:18,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--I'm so embarrassed!
--Quit kidding around.</b></font>

80
00:05:18,024 --> 00:05:22,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's too much money
for us to come up with.</b></font>

81
00:05:22,494 --> 00:05:24,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know that!</b></font>

82
00:05:24,504 --> 00:05:27,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was just wondering.</b></font>

83
00:05:27,004 --> 00:05:31,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You have no imagination.</b></font>

84
00:05:31,344 --> 00:05:34,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's too far off to imagine.</b></font>

85
00:05:35,674 --> 00:05:38,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We now know that Takumi's
technique is the real deal</b></font>

86
00:05:38,514 --> 00:05:41,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and will hold up anywhere.</b></font>

87
00:05:41,114 --> 00:05:43,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's more than just technique.</b></font>

88
00:05:43,854 --> 00:05:45,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Thank you very much.
--You need natural talent</b></font>

89
00:05:45,684 --> 00:05:49,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to be able to race well on a new course.</b></font>

90
00:05:49,354 --> 00:05:53,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's a genius because he
defeated all those modern cars</b></font>

91
00:05:53,194 --> 00:05:56,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>with his ten-year-old Eight-Six.</b></font>

92
00:05:56,134 --> 00:05:58,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--How gratifying!
--Get a load of you!</b></font>

93
00:05:58,804 --> 00:06:02,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're the one who said he
couldn't compete anywhere else</b></font>

94
00:06:02,474 --> 00:06:04,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>because he only knew Akina.</b></font>

95
00:06:04,644 --> 00:06:07,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know I did, but...</b></font>

96
00:06:07,474 --> 00:06:09,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We all thought that.</b></font>

97
00:06:09,314 --> 00:06:10,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi is abnormal.</b></font>

98
00:06:10,984 --> 00:06:14,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When I heard the news,
I was sure he'd lose at Usui</b></font>

99
00:06:14,654 --> 00:06:17,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>against Mako's Sileighty.</b></font>

100
00:06:18,554 --> 00:06:20,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sorry, Iketani.</b></font>

101
00:06:20,154 --> 00:06:22,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't worry about it.</b></font>

102
00:06:22,324 --> 00:06:26,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've decided to go by
"Iketani the Lonely Driver."</b></font>

103
00:06:26,994 --> 00:06:29,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That name sounds familiar.</b></font>

104
00:06:32,504 --> 00:06:34,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Welcome.</b></font>

105
00:06:35,934 --> 00:06:37,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Flowers?</b></font>

106
00:06:37,344 --> 00:06:40,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you sure this isn't a mistake?</b></font>

107
00:06:40,074 --> 00:06:42,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is a gas station...</b></font>

108
00:06:44,184 --> 00:06:46,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi, this is for you.</b></font>

109
00:06:46,984 --> 00:06:49,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who is it from?</b></font>

110
00:06:49,084 --> 00:06:50,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>From Ryosuke Takahashi.</b></font>

111
00:06:50,924 --> 00:06:53,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

112
00:06:53,324 --> 00:06:55,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke...</b></font>

113
00:06:55,154 --> 00:06:56,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...Takahashi.</b></font>

114
00:06:56,354 --> 00:06:59,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>From the number-one superstar in Gunma...</b></font>

115
00:06:59,594 --> 00:07:01,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...to Takumi!</b></font>

116
00:07:04,964 --> 00:07:06,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What does it say?</b></font>

117
00:07:06,804 --> 00:07:08,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let me see.</b></font>

118
00:07:07,974 --> 00:07:13,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"To Panda Trueno</b></font>

119
00:07:07,974 --> 00:07:13,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}9/15 10:00 PM, Mt. Akina Peak"</b></font>

120
00:07:08,604 --> 00:07:11,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>September 15th at 10 PM...</b></font>

121
00:07:11,804 --> 00:07:14,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...at the top of Mount Akina.</b></font>

122
00:07:16,374 --> 00:07:18,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is that all it says?</b></font>

123
00:07:18,484 --> 00:07:22,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It sounds like...</b></font>

124
00:07:22,214 --> 00:07:24,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's finally here.</b></font>

125
00:07:24,054 --> 00:07:25,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A challenge from Ryosuke Takahashi</b></font>

126
00:07:25,984 --> 00:07:28,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>for a downhill battle.</b></font>

127
00:07:28,794 --> 00:07:31,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow!</b></font>

128
00:07:31,194 --> 00:07:33,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you gonna do?</b></font>

129
00:07:33,024 --> 00:07:36,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You know he has to accept the challenge.</b></font>

130
00:07:36,694 --> 00:07:40,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi already smoked
Ryosuke's brother Keisuke.</b></font>

131
00:07:40,634 --> 00:07:43,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's right. Avoiding a rematch</b></font>

132
00:07:43,804 --> 00:07:46,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>is more humiliating than losing one.</b></font>

133
00:08:00,324 --> 00:08:02,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's the matter?</b></font>

134
00:08:02,824 --> 00:08:05,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't you like being with me?</b></font>

135
00:08:06,324 --> 00:08:11,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Of course I do!
--You seem uninterested and preoccupied.</b></font>

136
00:08:11,664 --> 00:08:14,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's normal, I guess.</b></font>

137
00:08:14,074 --> 00:08:17,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You seem so far away.</b></font>

138
00:08:17,034 --> 00:08:19,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If this isn't fun, we should go.</b></font>

139
00:08:19,544 --> 00:08:21,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It is fun!</b></font>

140
00:08:21,174 --> 00:08:24,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sorry, I apologize.</b></font>

141
00:08:24,184 --> 00:08:28,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll forgive you if you tell me
what you were thinking about.</b></font>

142
00:08:29,854 --> 00:08:34,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, I don't think you would really get it.</b></font>

143
00:08:36,054 --> 00:08:39,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Bye!
--Okay, I'll tell you!</b></font>

144
00:08:42,294 --> 00:08:43,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A battle?</b></font>

145
00:08:43,864 --> 00:08:47,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Yeah.
--Is that like a fistfight?</b></font>

146
00:08:47,104 --> 00:08:51,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No. A battle is a car race.</b></font>

147
00:08:51,704 --> 00:08:54,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A car race?</b></font>

148
00:08:56,314 --> 00:08:59,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I never knew that racing was your hobby.</b></font>

149
00:08:59,814 --> 00:09:05,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not really my hobby, but I
guess it's kind of become one.</b></font>

150
00:09:05,454 --> 00:09:10,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My next opponent is very
good and very well known.</b></font>

151
00:09:10,494 --> 00:09:14,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've been thinking about it since this morning.</b></font>

152
00:09:14,734 --> 00:09:18,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I must be feeling the pressure.</b></font>

153
00:09:18,004 --> 00:09:22,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're a good driver, so you'll be okay.</b></font>

154
00:09:22,074 --> 00:09:24,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not that easy.</b></font>

155
00:09:24,444 --> 00:09:27,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you don't want to race, just ignore him.</b></font>

156
00:09:27,814 --> 00:09:30,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not that I don't want to.</b></font>

157
00:09:30,144 --> 00:09:32,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I may lose to him,</b></font>

158
00:09:32,484 --> 00:09:34,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I don't want to not race him.</b></font>

159
00:09:36,514 --> 00:09:39,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's so like you.</b></font>

160
00:09:40,854 --> 00:09:43,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You want to do it deep down, don't you?</b></font>

161
00:09:43,854 --> 00:09:45,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You don't show it,</b></font>

162
00:09:45,864 --> 00:09:49,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I know you're very competitive.</b></font>

163
00:09:49,664 --> 00:09:53,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I kind of like that about you.</b></font>

164
00:10:05,544 --> 00:10:07,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ready to go?</b></font>

165
00:10:10,554 --> 00:10:15,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why don't we talk a little more before we go?</b></font>

166
00:10:15,494 --> 00:10:17,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure.</b></font>

167
00:10:42,214 --> 00:10:50,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know why you got in a fight
with that senior in the locker room.</b></font>

168
00:10:52,024 --> 00:10:54,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After you quit the team,</b></font>

169
00:10:54,394 --> 00:10:57,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>your teammate told me why.</b></font>

170
00:10:57,704 --> 00:11:02,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You stood up for me, didn't you?</b></font>

171
00:11:05,744 --> 00:11:09,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sorry I misunderstood you.</b></font>

172
00:11:09,744 --> 00:11:11,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't be.</b></font>

173
00:11:11,914 --> 00:11:16,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It doesn't matter now.</b></font>

174
00:12:25,454 --> 00:12:27,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's Takumi's Eight-Six.</b></font>

175
00:12:29,194 --> 00:12:31,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who is that girl?</b></font>

176
00:13:02,954 --> 00:13:06,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Man, Keiichi Tsuchiya's drift is incredible!</b></font>

177
00:13:06,864 --> 00:13:08,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Look.</b></font>

178
00:13:08,164 --> 00:13:11,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Look at these pictures.</b></font>

179
00:13:11,204 --> 00:13:14,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi? Hey, Takumi!</b></font>

180
00:13:15,504 --> 00:13:19,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What is it, Itsuki? Lunchtime?</b></font>

181
00:13:19,304 --> 00:13:20,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You idiot!</b></font>

182
00:13:22,344 --> 00:13:25,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sorry, I was just talking to myself.</b></font>

183
00:13:28,584 --> 00:13:31,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi's been acting weird?</b></font>

184
00:13:31,384 --> 00:13:33,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's so weird?</b></font>

185
00:13:33,824 --> 00:13:35,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He seems out of it.</b></font>

186
00:13:35,494 --> 00:13:37,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's normal.</b></font>

187
00:13:37,154 --> 00:13:41,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know, but he was better during the summer.</b></font>

188
00:13:41,864 --> 00:13:45,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But when school started,</b></font>

189
00:13:45,034 --> 00:13:49,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>he suddenly got even worse than before.</b></font>

190
00:13:49,004 --> 00:13:52,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Tired from all the races?</b></font>

191
00:13:52,344 --> 00:13:55,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He just started racing this summer.</b></font>

192
00:13:55,614 --> 00:14:00,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He may have lost his focus because of school.</b></font>

193
00:14:00,714 --> 00:14:04,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't think that's it.</b></font>

194
00:14:04,554 --> 00:14:08,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's like something in his head broke.</b></font>

195
00:14:08,524 --> 00:14:11,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is he gonna be able to race like that?</b></font>

196
00:14:14,364 --> 00:14:17,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He has a girlfriend, doesn't he?</b></font>

197
00:14:17,804 --> 00:14:20,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you talking about?</b></font>

198
00:14:20,604 --> 00:14:24,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just thought he might
be daydreaming about her.</b></font>

199
00:14:24,744 --> 00:14:26,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Daydreaming?</b></font>

200
00:14:26,974 --> 00:14:30,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just like how you were with Mako...</b></font>

201
00:14:30,944 --> 00:14:35,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kenji... that name is taboo here.</b></font>

202
00:14:35,884 --> 00:14:39,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's all right, Itsuki.</b></font>

203
00:14:40,994 --> 00:14:45,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, I happened to see
Takumi driving with a girl.</b></font>

204
00:14:45,664 --> 00:14:48,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you serious?!</b></font>

205
00:14:48,094 --> 00:14:52,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just got a glimpse, but she was pretty.</b></font>

206
00:14:52,564 --> 00:14:55,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi's girlfriend...</b></font>

207
00:15:05,244 --> 00:15:10,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No wonder he's been
ditching me after school lately.</b></font>

208
00:15:10,014 --> 00:15:12,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That traitor!</b></font>

209
00:15:12,984 --> 00:15:17,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've never even held a girl's hand!</b></font>

210
00:15:17,494 --> 00:15:20,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's it! That must be the reason!</b></font>

211
00:15:20,324 --> 00:15:21,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm positive!</b></font>

212
00:15:21,764 --> 00:15:23,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Leave it to me!</b></font>

213
00:15:23,594 --> 00:15:26,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll take him out and interrogate him!</b></font>

214
00:15:26,464 --> 00:15:30,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Racers don't need girls, right, Iketani?!</b></font>

215
00:15:30,674 --> 00:15:32,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right!</b></font>

216
00:15:32,504 --> 00:15:36,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We are the "Lonely Drivers"!</b></font>

217
00:15:36,474 --> 00:15:38,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is sad.</b></font>

218
00:15:56,294 --> 00:15:59,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's on your mind?</b></font>

219
00:15:59,704 --> 00:16:01,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You've been...</b></font>

220
00:16:01,704 --> 00:16:05,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...dating Mogi behind my
back lately, haven't you?</b></font>

221
00:16:07,544 --> 00:16:09,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, is that all?</b></font>

222
00:16:09,514 --> 00:16:10,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"Is that all"?!</b></font>

223
00:16:10,744 --> 00:16:13,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's no secret.</b></font>

224
00:16:13,014 --> 00:16:16,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But nothing special to tell, either.</b></font>

225
00:16:16,014 --> 00:16:19,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No excuses! Just answer this question...</b></font>

226
00:16:20,824 --> 00:16:24,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How far did you go?</b></font>

227
00:16:24,994 --> 00:16:29,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Honestly, how far did you guys go?</b></font>

228
00:16:29,194 --> 00:16:30,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How far?</b></font>

229
00:16:30,894 --> 00:16:33,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Be honest with your best friend!</b></font>

230
00:16:33,364 --> 00:16:35,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Itsuki, watch out!</b></font>

231
00:16:40,704 --> 00:16:42,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll tell you!</b></font>

232
00:16:42,214 --> 00:16:44,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then tell me!</b></font>

233
00:16:44,844 --> 00:16:46,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Last Sunday...</b></font>

234
00:16:46,284 --> 00:16:48,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sunday!</b></font>

235
00:16:48,514 --> 00:16:51,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...the two of us...</b></font>

236
00:16:51,284 --> 00:16:52,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The two of you...!</b></font>

237
00:16:52,884 --> 00:16:54,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...went to Akina Lake.</b></font>

238
00:16:56,224 --> 00:16:59,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Itsuki, watch out!</b></font>

239
00:17:02,694 --> 00:17:04,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What I mean is...</b></font>

240
00:17:04,964 --> 00:17:08,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...which base did you get to, you idiot?</b></font>

241
00:17:08,974 --> 00:17:11,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Which base?</b></font>

242
00:17:13,204 --> 00:17:16,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Did you kiss her?</b></font>

243
00:17:16,774 --> 00:17:20,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Sure.
--What?!</b></font>

244
00:17:20,144 --> 00:17:22,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Itsuki, stop!</b></font>

245
00:17:22,554 --> 00:17:24,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Stop the car!</b></font>

246
00:17:30,624 --> 00:17:34,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Yeah, he's daydreaming about her.</i></b></font>

247
00:17:34,324 --> 00:17:36,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why are you staring at me?</b></font>

248
00:17:36,434 --> 00:17:38,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You've been weird lately.</b></font>

249
00:17:38,664 --> 00:17:40,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have?</b></font>

250
00:17:40,564 --> 00:17:42,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You never think much,</b></font>

251
00:17:42,634 --> 00:17:46,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>yet you've been so preoccupied.</b></font>

252
00:17:46,144 --> 00:17:49,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess so.</b></font>

253
00:17:49,314 --> 00:17:54,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He probably can't stop</i>
<i>thinking about Mogi's soft lips.</i></b></font>

254
00:17:54,984 --> 00:17:57,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've been wondering...</b></font>

255
00:17:57,184 --> 00:18:00,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...what's gonna happen to us in the future.</b></font>

256
00:18:00,824 --> 00:18:03,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In the future?!</b></font>

257
00:18:03,154 --> 00:18:05,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>After kissing comes...</i></b></font>

258
00:18:05,624 --> 00:18:09,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How can you even bring up
such a shameful subject</b></font>

259
00:18:09,194 --> 00:18:12,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>in front of the "Lonely Driver"?!</b></font>

260
00:18:12,204 --> 00:18:15,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's only one thing left to do after kissing!</b></font>

261
00:18:17,374 --> 00:18:20,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's the one thing?</b></font>

262
00:18:20,044 --> 00:18:21,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You know--<i>it</i>!</b></font>

263
00:18:21,974 --> 00:18:23,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you talking about?!</b></font>

264
00:18:23,844 --> 00:18:25,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're not making any sense.</b></font>

265
00:18:25,844 --> 00:18:29,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What I mean by the future is...</b></font>

266
00:18:29,984 --> 00:18:35,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Never mind. Difficult thoughts
aren't my specialty.</b></font>

267
00:18:35,124 --> 00:18:39,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It looks like his daydreaming</i>
<i>can't be easily fixed.</i></b></font>

268
00:18:39,364 --> 00:18:46,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Welcome to Touge</b></font>

269
00:18:39,364 --> 00:18:46,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}Altitude: 1434m"</b></font>

270
00:19:09,824 --> 00:19:11,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No wonder.</b></font>

271
00:19:11,164 --> 00:19:14,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's Keisuke's FD and Kenta's S14.</b></font>

272
00:19:14,264 --> 00:19:16,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kenta is fast down the hill.</b></font>

273
00:19:16,694 --> 00:19:20,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>His non-turbo S14 is made for it.</b></font>

274
00:19:20,204 --> 00:19:22,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke took him under his wing</b></font>

275
00:19:22,374 --> 00:19:25,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and has been personally training him.</b></font>

276
00:19:25,044 --> 00:19:28,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's our number-two successor.</b></font>

277
00:19:32,614 --> 00:19:35,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The battle against the
Night Kids is in two days.</b></font>

278
00:19:35,854 --> 00:19:39,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke shouldn't be wasting time with Kenta.</b></font>

279
00:19:39,354 --> 00:19:41,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He must be confident.</b></font>

280
00:19:41,794 --> 00:19:45,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess Takeshi Nakazato is easy prey.</b></font>

281
00:19:45,264 --> 00:19:48,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke's on fire lately.</b></font>

282
00:19:48,894 --> 00:19:52,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't you think he's been
driving like Ryosuke lately?</b></font>

283
00:19:52,734 --> 00:19:55,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, I noticed that, too.</b></font>

284
00:19:55,734 --> 00:20:00,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke must be feeling pretty
confident about his brother.</b></font>

285
00:20:00,974 --> 00:20:04,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I heard that's why he's not coming to Myogi.</b></font>

286
00:20:16,424 --> 00:20:20,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can I ask you one thing, Keisuke?</b></font>

287
00:20:20,624 --> 00:20:22,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What is it?</b></font>

288
00:20:22,094 --> 00:20:25,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why aren't we challenging the Eight-Six?</b></font>

289
00:20:25,104 --> 00:20:29,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We should have him
come to Akagi for revenge.</b></font>

290
00:20:30,334 --> 00:20:32,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Akagi, huh?
--Sure!</b></font>

291
00:20:32,904 --> 00:20:38,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's no way you'll lose
to the Eight-Six on our turf.</b></font>

292
00:20:38,414 --> 00:20:40,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you won't do it...</b></font>

293
00:20:40,844 --> 00:20:42,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...I will!</b></font>

294
00:20:42,284 --> 00:20:44,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Forget it, Kenta.
--Why?</b></font>

295
00:20:44,754 --> 00:20:47,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You think he'll beat me?</b></font>

296
00:20:47,084 --> 00:20:48,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not on Akagi's downhill.</b></font>

297
00:20:48,924 --> 00:20:51,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's beside the point.</b></font>

298
00:20:51,864 --> 00:20:55,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're a Red Sun now, and don't forget it.</b></font>

299
00:20:55,694 --> 00:21:00,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We race on our opponents' courses.</b></font>

300
00:21:00,334 --> 00:21:02,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know we do...</b></font>

301
00:21:02,674 --> 00:21:05,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...but I can't take it.</b></font>

302
00:21:05,344 --> 00:21:07,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six got the best of us!</b></font>

303
00:21:07,974 --> 00:21:11,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If only we could battle fair and square...</b></font>

304
00:21:11,944 --> 00:21:14,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please let me take him!</b></font>

305
00:21:14,614 --> 00:21:16,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Be patient!</b></font>

306
00:21:21,654 --> 00:21:23,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't worry.</b></font>

307
00:21:23,494 --> 00:21:25,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When the opportunity arises,</b></font>

308
00:21:25,894 --> 00:21:30,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the person who needs to put
an end to it will do just that.</b></font>

309
00:21:30,394 --> 00:21:32,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You mean...</b></font>

310
00:21:32,134 --> 00:21:34,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...Ryosuke will?</b></font>

311
00:21:34,834 --> 00:21:38,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Be patient. First, the Night Kids race.</b></font>

312
00:21:38,004 --> 00:21:40,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just leave everything to us.</b></font>

313
00:22:02,264 --> 00:22:04,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He does seem weird.</b></font>

314
00:22:04,094 --> 00:22:07,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>See?! He confessed.</b></font>

315
00:22:07,034 --> 00:22:09,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He is, indeed, daydreaming.</b></font>

316
00:22:09,034 --> 00:22:11,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We gotta do something.</b></font>

317
00:22:11,034 --> 00:22:15,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We only have one week until the big race.</b></font>

